prodNameC: "西門子"甲狀腺刺激荷爾蒙3試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
(1) ADVIA Centaur TSH-3: lite reagent, solid phase,  low calibrator, high calibrator
(2) ACS: 180 TSH-3: lite reagent, solid phase,  low calibrator, high calibrator
lite reagent: monoclonal mouse anti-TSH antibody (0.3 ug/mL)labeled with acridinium ester in HEPES buffered saline.
solid phase: polyclonal sheep anti-TSH antibody (53 ug/mL) covalently coupled to paramagnetic particles in HEPES buffered saline.
calibrators: after reconstitution, low and high levels of TSH in HEPES buffered equine serum.
(3) master curve material: various levels of thyroid-stimulating hormone in lyophilized equine serum.
